MULTILINGUAL CHAT APPLICATION
============================

Quick Start Guide
-----------------

1. INSTALL OLLAMA:
   - Download from: https://ollama.ai
   - Run: ollama pull llama3.2
   - Start: ollama serve

2. INSTALL DEPENDENCIES:
   - Run: pip install -r requirements.txt

3. START APPLICATION:
   - Windows: Double-click start.bat
   - Linux/Mac: ./start.sh
   - Manual: python app.py

4. OPEN BROWSER:
   - Go to: http://localhost:5000

FEATURES:
- Real-time chat with automatic translation
- Support for 8+ languages including English and Hindi
- Multiple chat rooms
- Modern responsive UI
- Live user presence

TROUBLESHOOTING:
- If Ollama fails: Check if ollama serve is running
- If port 5000 busy: Kill process or change port in app.py
- Translation issues: Verify ollama model is installed

For detailed documentation, see README.md